text: Kathryn Kimball Mizelle (born 1987)United States Senate Committee on the Judiciary: Questionnaire for Judicial Nominees: Kathryn Mizelle is an American politician and lawyer. She is a United States District Judge of the United States District Court for the Middle District of Florida since 2020. At age 33, she was the youngest person chosen by President Donald Trump for a lifetime judge term.Senate confirms Trump's youngest federal judge to serve in Tampa, Tampa Bay Times, Jamal Thalji, November 18, 2020.
